wikipedia_page.main: Sean Taylor (born 9 December 1985 in Wansbeck, Northumberland) is an English footballer who last played as a midfielder in the Football League for Blackpool, while on loan from Sunderland, for whom he did not make a first-team appearance. He moved into non-League football with Ashington in January 2007.
